{"tid":1542380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［推上熱門］想自保但又想要831 cctv?快入","createTime":"2019-09-04T23:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T08:38:07.000Z","uid":176484,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"94bf86a3854279787bb01afa69945c0f33a74efd","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:56:10.000Z","msg":"[律師建議］ 緊急 請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n831太子站當日有份俾人打嘅市民，請盡快聯絡律師做民事訴訟(personal injuries)，向法庭申請要地鐵攞CCTV。<br />\n<br />\n一定要快，如果過咗期限，地鐵話自動洗咗啲CCTV，到時就真係冇人知道太子發生過咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n註：其實唔止身體受傷，心靈受創都可以告。當日喺現場目擊事件，造成精神痛苦，都可以嘗試用 secondary victim （非直接受害人）去追討。最後告唔告得入唔係最重要，目的係令多啲人有權拎CCTV，還原真相⚠️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟 98190979<br />\n民陣 65499452<br />\n民權觀察 94632945<br />\n伍展邦律師行 26081400<br />\n<br />\n推呀！！唔想有人抄車，但更加唔想抄左車但冇人知！！黑警一定要還債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追究到底！啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">想自保都有野幫到手!</span></span></strong><br />\n如果想自保，請所有知情人士立即錄影一片短片(遮樣，但一定要仔細描述當時情況)，將你所知既細節送去各大媒體，並響9月5日中午12點前，以匿名方式送到各大媒體(報章、社交媒體)。當呢件事徹底曝光，響公眾既注視下，你地先會真正既安全<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em>知道你地可能有好多各方面擔心  但想知真相得一個方法 就係拎到cctv 唔想搞民氏訴訟 都幫手拍條片send去各大媒體啊</em></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">求下你地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />盡力幫幫手</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果拎到 我地離革命成功 又遇進一大步ga啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b1d5ac7e8ee6cef86848eb691001537251d4fa1d","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:56:28.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"b9bb1d260a94fe9579b433afccc123eeef0a55cb","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:56:40.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"8b16c2556dc2d621e9e8d08b064286d173516d9e","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:56:53.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"3c82da9d6ecad80b7df39be44895e25d0fedd7d4","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:57:03.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"716c7d78fadad6e832c2ea2eb2d12fe445d58039","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:57:15.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"46ef4924dc761c0629f15d5a5aaabdd677a3788c","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:57:25.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"71590239246b211ff88406e2f6bd0289a20ed061","tid":1542380,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:57:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e96fa5ea62d3e5eb7cf63cefe31dd9d99095ebe","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:57:37.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"bbe384444e0ab8f1a40b7040bae820939ed69f17","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:57:48.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"608836d276a7f44f491fca1c000925d87312e7a5","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:58:06.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"6de9d5ce2e82f1f17f79fbba8ad9a2addfeebab0","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:58:17.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"f1fac921f3c7