既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"689efa440892c1c36024efe2ee90f578e9dccf71","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:08:05.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"c9e459a60358bb0a2811e11292d1a91d992cf7ab","tid":1542380,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:08:17.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"7063a994ad842242e48bef7ad486d7721afbd017","tid":1542380,"uid":208391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:08:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fbecddf09a6bdb74b729ffea2d9a4afcc1c02e85","tid":1542380,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:08:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f9ce69a7c00485dc22fefd66c9884303f307de1","tid":1542380,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:08:34.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"39c4de56b62cb097f7552e67a884c660b41c69dc","tid":1542380,"uid":114937,"like":0,"disli